{"tid":1505162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又多2個]兩男子涉元朗襲擊暫控參與暴動　明日粉嶺法院提堂","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:53:00.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1417e793c467e006744cd6448ffb1be45557dfe6","tid":1505162,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"元朗西鐵站7.21襲擊事件，其中兩名被捕男子被暫控參與暴動罪，案件明日下午於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有兩名同樣涉及元朗襲擊事件的男子被控參與暴動，他們暫時毋須答辯，獲准保釋，等候案件在10月25日再訊。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3564f888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=79cd1230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e91ebaf289d817011163c24f0d3d51f858d385f4","tid":1505162,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dfb028d7021cc75d6a769629d50555b78e2e14e6","tid":1505162,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1417e793c467e006744cd6448ffb1be45557dfe6","tid":1505162,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"元朗西鐵站7.21襲擊事件，其中兩名被捕男子被暫控參與暴動罪，案件明日下午於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有兩名同樣涉及元朗襲擊事件的男子被控參與暴動，他們暫時毋須答辯，獲准保釋，等候案件在10月25日再訊。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3564f888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=79cd1230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"裁判法院的最高刑罰一般為監禁2年和罰款10萬元。但是，當法庭同時處理兩項或以上的可公訴罪行時，裁判官可判處最高3年的刑期。就某些條例而言，單一罪行可判處監禁3年和罰款500萬元。<br />\n<br />\n天琦就高等法院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af333b4a333122fbdf358650c2769a3da1c2ae94","tid":1505162,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d42c7aab2b0863eaca680bb9ab4a92a85d203a2","tid":1505162,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb028d7021cc75d6a769629d50555b78e2e14e6","tid":1505162,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1417e793c467e006744cd6448ffb1be45557dfe6","tid":1505162,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"元朗西鐵站7.21襲擊事件，其中兩名被捕男子被暫控參與暴動罪，案件明日下午於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有兩名同樣涉及元朗襲擊事件的男子被控參與暴動，他們暫時毋須答辯，獲准保釋，等候案件在10月25日再訊。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=3564f888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476684-20190825.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=79cd1230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476684-20190825.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:40.